      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted hemolysis index must agree with experimental measurements within combined model and experimental uncertainty bands at all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis predictions fall within experimental uncertainty bounds at 4 of 5 operating points; 1 point shows 7% deviation within expanded uncertainty. Gradation 3 achieved."
