      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs extracted from the model must directly correspond to the clinical hemolysis metrics used in the regulatory decision.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) and normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) are the primary QoIs, directly corresponding to FDA guidance metrics. Sensitivity analysis confirms these are the dominant outputs. Gradation 4 achieved."
